subSubSection.paragraph:
Pleuroptya quadrimaculalis
: Bae, 2001: 122-124, pl. 5 fig. 172; 
Park et al. 2007
: 177, 239 fig. 94; 
Bae et al. 2008
: 148-149, fig. 167.

Our identification of this species is based on characters of external morphology (
Motschulsky 1861
; 
Inoue 1982
; Li et al. 2012; 
Sasaki and Yamanaka 2013
; 
Lu and Du 2020
) and male genitalia (Li et al. 2012; 
Lu and Du 2020
). The species status was confirmed by DNA barcodes.
